summary: As much as I hate Dio with a burning passion, to the point he makes my blood BOIL, his OVA design meets all my standards so I...
body:
As much as I hate Dio with a burning passion, to the point he makes my blood BOIL, his OVA design meets all my standards so I had to draw him. Not the best scene redraw, but I had fun honestly! Wow looking at it now, I notice I draw my eyes huge.

[Reposts are welcome as long as you credit me!]

💕Reblogs MUCH Appreciated!💕
